      <title>交易员考虑美联储降息押注，美元持稳；日元兑 150/dlr 走势不稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-ponder-fed-rate-cut-bets-yen-shaky-150dlr-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示美国通胀依然粘性但逐渐放缓，周五美元保持稳定，保留了美联储6月降息的机会，而日元则回落至150兑美元的关键水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-ponder-fed-rate-cut-bets-yen-shaky-150dlr-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 01:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称越南计划打击工人权利和对外援助</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-eyes-crackdown-workers-rights-foreign-aid-report-says-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一个倡导组织称，在越南准备扩大工人权利之际，执政的共产党已指示官员控制工会，同时密切监视外国组织和出国旅行的公民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-eyes-crackdown-workers-rights-foreign-aid-report-says-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 01:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国2月出口增长超出芯片需求预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korean-february-export-growth-beats-forecasts-chip-demand-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国贸易部周五公布的数据显示，韩国 2 月份出口增长超出市场预期，连续第五个月增长，原因是半导体需求激增弥补了汽车销量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korean-february-export-growth-beats-forecasts-chip-demand-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 00:47:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一些美国议员敦促拜登、布林肯不要承认巴基斯坦新政府</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/some-us-lawmakers-urge-biden-blinken-not-recognize-new-pakistan-government-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三十一名美国国会议员签署了一封致总统乔·拜登和国务卿安东尼·布林肯的信，敦促他们在对选举干预进行调查之前不要承认巴基斯坦新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/some-us-lawmakers-urge-biden-blinken-not-recognize-new-pakistan-government-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 00:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理支持间谍首席决定不点名“出卖”的前政客</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pm-supports-spy-chief-decision-not-name-ex-politician-who-sold-out-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯周五表示，他支持间谍头子不点名一名“出卖”外国情报机构的前政客的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pm-supports-spy-chief-decision-not-name-ex-politician-who-sold-out-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 23:33:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰燃油泵的“闰年故障”现已修复</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/leap-year-glitch-new-zealand-fuel-pumps-now-fixed-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该软件背后的公司在周五的一份声明中表示，由于支付软件的“闰年故障”，新西兰的汽油泵于周四停止工作，现在大部分已恢复运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/leap-year-glitch-new-zealand-fuel-pumps-now-fixed-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 22:43:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰央行表示政策需要在一段时间内保持限制性</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/new-zealand-central-bank-says-policy-needs-stay-restrictive-some-time-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位央行行长周五表示，新西兰的利率需要在一段时间内保持限制性，以确保通胀预期再次完全稳定，同时强调他们没有考虑降息的“心态”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/new-zealand-central-bank-says-policy-needs-stay-restrictive-some-time-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 22:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
